items.title: CapRock Partners acquires industrial facility in Sky Harbor market
items.summary:
CapRock Partners, a leading private industrial real estate investment firm based in Orange County, California, today announced that it has acquired a distribution/manufacturing facility in the highly sought after Sky Harbor submarket of Phoenix, Arizona, in an off-market transaction. items.title: Tucson’s World View accomplishes 27-hour mission with space balloon
items.summary:
A Tucson-based aerospace company that is using high altitude balloons to reach the stars in lieu of rockets just reached a major milestone when its stratospheric balloon, Stratollite, successfully accomplished a 27-hour mission.  In late August, World View launched its Stratollite craft from Page, Arizona with four remote sensing payloads from Ball Aerospace. Stratollite hung in the air for a full day and night cycle. This was the longestâ€¦ Read More â†’
